OL,6,FAhmed Ebid was working with people-
OL,7,Fsmuggling networks to organise boats,
OL,8,Fbringing over hundreds of migrants at
OL,9,Fa time on extremely dangerous vessels,
OL,10,FITV News Correspondent Neil Connery
OL,11,Freports
OL,13,FA London-based people smuggler who
OL,14,Fhelped "ruthlessly and cynically"
OL,15,Fexploit migrants as part of a #12
OL,16,Fmillion illegal boat crossing
OL,17,Foperation has been jailed for 25 years.
