OL,3,CPeople smuggler who 'managed' #12m
OL,4,Cboat crossings jailed for 25 years
OL,6,FEgyptian-born Ahmed Ebid, 42, helped
OL,7,Forganise the movement of nearly 3,800
OL,8,Fmigrants ` including women and
OL,9,Fchildren ` on just seven fishing boat
OL,10,Fcrossings from North Africa to Italy
OL,11,Fbetween October 2022 and June 2023 and
OL,12,Fsome of them made their way to
OL,13,FBritain, the National Crime Agency
OL,14,F(NCA) said.
OL,16,FEbid even told an associate to kill
OL,17,Fand throw into the sea any migrants
OL,18,Fcaught with phones, in a bid to avoid
OL,19,Flaw enforcement, the NCA said ` all
OL,20,Fwhile he was living in Isleworth.
