OL,6,FReacting to the sentence, Prime
OL,7,FMinister Sir Keir Starmer said on X:
OL,8,F"Good. I am determined to smash the
OL,9,Fsmall boat gangs behind the vile trade
OL,10,Fin people smuggling."
OL,12,FJudge Adam Hiddleston said that Ebid
OL,13,Fhad a "significant managerial role
OL,14,Fwithin an organised crime group" and
OL,15,Fthat his "primary motivation was to
OL,16,Fmake money out of human trafficking".
