OL,6,FThe judge told Ebid the "conspiracy
OL,7,Fthat you were a part of generated
OL,8,Fmillions of pounds" and that he must
OL,9,Fhave been a "beneficiary" of "a
OL,10,Fsignificant amount".
OL,12,FHe added that the "truly staggering"
OL,13,Famount of money came from the "hard-
OL,14,Fearned savings of desperate
OL,15,Findividuals", who were "ruthlessly and
OL,16,Fcynically exploited" by Ebid and the
OL,17,Fcrime group.
