OL,6,FThe judge said "exploitation on such
OL,7,Fan enormous scale" causes "so much
OL,8,Fmisery" and "could so easily lead to a
OL,9,Fconsiderable loss of life".
OL,11,FThe judge also said: "The treatment of
OL,12,Fthe migrants on your orders and in
OL,13,Fyour name was horrifying. They were
OL,14,Fsimply a commodity to you.
OL,16,F"You talked of them in terms of units,
OL,17,Fnot as people, referring to them as
OL,18,F'cartons'.
