OL,6,F"The important thing to you was that
OL,7,Feach paid up the exorbitant fare that
OL,8,Fwas charged for their crossing and
OL,9,Fthat nobody did anything to compromise
OL,10,Fyour operation ` such as by carrying a
OL,11,Fmobile phone.
OL,13,F"As we know, if they did, you were
OL,14,Fprepared to instruct others to
OL,15,Fthreaten them with death. You
OL,16,Fdemonstrated no empathy or care
OL,17,Fwhatsoever for these desperate and
OL,18,Fvulnerable men, women and children. "
