OL,6,FEbid arrived in the UK in October 2022
OL,7,Fafter crossing the Channel in a small
OL,8,Fboat, having been sentenced in Italy
OL,9,Fin 2017 to a total of six years and
OL,10,Ftwo months in prison for drug-
OL,11,Fsmuggling.
OL,13,FSoon afterwards, he began arranging
OL,14,Fthe operations in the Mediterranean.
OL,16,FHe was working with people-smuggling
OL,17,Fnetworks to organise boats, bringing
OL,18,Fover hundreds of migrants at a time on
OL,19,Fextremely dangerous vessels from Libya
OL,20,Fand advertising the crossings on
OL,21,FFacebook.
