OL,6,FEbid sourced and provided boats and
OL,7,Fcrews, provided technical advice
OL,8,Fduring the crossings, helped house
OL,9,Fmigrants, and dealt with any required
OL,10,Fpaperwork, prosecutors said.
OL,12,FIn one conversation with an associate,
OL,13,Frecorded via a listening device
OL,14,Fplanted by NCA officers, he said
OL,15,Fmigrants were not to carry phones with
OL,16,Fthem on his boats.
OL,18,FHe said: "Tell them guys anyone caught
OL,19,Fwith a phone will be killed, threw in
OL,20,Fthe sea."
