OL,6,FOne crossing on October 25 2022 saw
OL,7,Fmore than 640 migrants rescued by the
OL,8,FItalian authorities after they
OL,9,Fattempted to cross in a wooden boat,
OL,10,Fthe NCA said.
OL,12,FIt was taken into port in Sicily and
OL,13,Ftwo bodies were recovered.
OL,15,FIn another, 265 migrants were rescued
OL,16,Fby the Italian coastguard from a 20m
OL,17,F(66ft) fishing boat found adrift in
OL,18,Fthe Mediterranean in early December
OL,19,F2022 after it left Benghazi.
