OL,6,FTwo search and rescue operations
OL,7,Foccurred in April 2023 after distress
OL,8,Fcalls to the coastguard and in each
OL,9,Fcase more than 600 migrants were on
OL,10,Fboard the boats, the NCA said.
OL,12,FEbid helped with at least seven
OL,13,Fseparate crossings which carried 3,781
OL,14,Fpeople into Italian waters.
OL,16,FEach migrant had been charged an
OL,17,Faverage of around #3,200, netting
OL,18,Fthose involved #12.3 million, the NCA
OL,19,Fsaid.
