OL,6,FEbid was detained in Isleworth in June
OL,7,F2023 after the NCA, along with the
OL,8,FItalian Guardia di Finanza and the
OL,9,FItalian coastguard, linked him to the
OL,10,Fcrossings.
OL,12,FOn a phone seized from him,
OL,13,Finvestigators found pictures of boats,
OL,14,Fconversations about the possible
OL,15,Fpurchase of vessels, videos of
OL,16,Fmigrants making the journey, and
OL,17,Fscreenshots of money transfers.
