OL,6,FTim Burton, specialist prosecutor for
OL,7,Fthe Crown Prosecution Service, said:
OL,8,F"Ahmed Ebid played a leading role in a
OL,9,Fsophisticated operation, which
OL,10,Fbreached immigration laws and
OL,11,Fendangered lives, for his own and
OL,12,Fothers' financial gain.
OL,14,F"Vulnerable people were transported on
OL,15,Flong sea journeys in ill-equipped
OL,16,Ffishing vessels completely unsuitable
OL,17,Ffor carrying the large number of
OL,18,Fpassengers who were on board.
OL,26,@pD@AOUvD@AOU
