OL,3,CPeople smuggler who 'managed' #12m
OL,4,Cboat crossings jailed for 25 years
OL,6,F"His repeated involvement in helping
OL,7,Fto facilitate these dangerous
OL,8,Fcrossings showed a complete disregard
OL,9,Ffor the safety of thousands of people,
OL,10,Fwhose lives were put at serious risk."
OL,12,FJacque Beer, of the NCA, said: "Ebid
OL,13,Fwas part of a crime network who preyed
OL,14,Fupon the desperation of migrants to
OL,15,Fship them across the Mediterranean in
OL,16,Fdeath-trap boats.
OL,18,F"The cruel nature of his business was
OL,19,Fdemonstrated by the callous way he
OL,20,Fspoke of throwing migrants into the
OL,21,Fsea if they didn't follow his rules.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@fO]tD@`OUzD@AOU
