OL,3,CPeople smuggler who 'managed' #12m
OL,4,Cboat crossings jailed for 25 years
OL,6,F"To him they were just a source of
OL,7,Fprofit.
OL,9,F"He was based in the UK but organising
OL,10,Fcrossings from North Africa.
OL,12,F"A proportion of those he moved to
OL,13,FItaly would also have ended up in
OL,14,Fnorthern Europe, attempting to cross
OL,15,Fthe Channel to the UK."
OL,17,FHome Office minister Dame Angela Eagle
OL,18,Fsaid: "For too long our borders have
OL,19,Fbeen undermined by vile people-
OL,20,Fsmuggling gangs putting lives at risk
OL,21,Ffor cash.
